main event: Two objects were observed over Long Beach, New York, on 31 October 1958; one round yellow object and one triangular red object.
interesting points: The two objects were reported to be the size of jets., The observation lasted for 4-5 seconds., The sighting occurred in clear skies., Both objects were seen moving from South-southeast to South., Local witnesses included a rabbi and his wife.
sighted object: one round yellow object and one triangular red object
